title: 250: Our Quarantine Vacation Mishaps | Ear Biscuits Ep.250
description:
Bloody ice cream, an unexpected addiction, and a thrown out back. These are just some of the happenings that R&L encounter on their vacation. Listen to the guys catch up on their isolated vacations, a new Rhett obsession, and even a never-before-heard backstory behind Commercial Kings - all on this bonus-filled episode of Ear Biscuits!
